<servinfo servinfosgmlid = "AENCP70A5206001" svcinfotypenbr = "08" svcinfoqualnbr = "03" page = "2" supplyoff = "1" modify = "0">
<title>
Manual Transaxle Oil Level Check
</title>
<s1 page = "2">
<ptxt>
Hoist vehicle and check manual transaxle for oil leakage. Repair leaky point, if any.
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1 page = "2">
<ptxt>
Remove oil level / filler plug (1). Check oil contamination and check that oil level is lower end of oil level / filler plug hole (2).
</ptxt>
<ptxt>
If oil is excessively dirty or insufficient, change oil or replenish specified oil up to plug hole.
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1 page = "2">
<ptxt>
Apply sealant to thread of level / filler plug, and then tighten it to specified torque.
</ptxt>
